data.description: Prepare to be impressed! This immaculate home located in Crosswinds Subdivision is waiting on YOU!! The moment you step inside you're sure to fall in love. The high ceilings and natural light are warm and inviting giving off the true feeling of home. With over 2,200 square feet, 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, formal dining, custom kitchen with breakfast area, all flowing seamlessly into the gracious living room, this is not only the perfect family home, it's also ideal for entertaining.  Enjoy the upcoming summer months in style while soaking up the sun in the newly installed pool or stay cool relaxing on the screened in porch.  This beauty will not last long so be sure and call today to schedule a tour!
